						<p>In modern characters. Refers to one Abhinavapūrṇapriya Śrīnivāsa Rao Sāhēb, Jagirdār of Ārṇi, piously performed the ceremony <hi rend="italic">ashṭabhandhana-kumbhābhishēka</hi> of Kanakagīrīśvara on this day, i.e., 27th November 1888 A.D.</p>						

